00:40:56.710 --> 00:40:57.560
Không có?

881
00:40:58.080 --> 00:41:00.150
Cha, cha xem mẹ kìa.

882
00:41:00.790 --> 00:41:01.520
Phu nhân,

883
00:41:01.750 --> 00:41:03.750
chúng ta mới về,
